Authentication

1. create project from firebase
2. app register from firebase
3. install firebse
4. firebase config filse add this project firebase folder
5. firebase config export app
6. firebase enable emial and passwrod method and others methods
7. create context folder and UserContext components file
8. create AuthContxt 
9. index.js file a UserContext vitore app.js rakte hobe
10. UserContext compnents a props hisabe children receive kora
11. AuthContext.Provider ar vitore children rakte hobe
12. Authcontext.Provider ar value hisabe userInfo ke pathano
13. context ta export kora and all pages theke import kore use kora
14. import auth and getAuth parameter ar vitor fireabse ar config ar app import kora
15. 